               <msContents>
                  <summary>In Minasian collection, there are 19 manuscripts under the generic title of Adʿīyah [Prayers]. The reason is that their individual titles have remained unknown for different reasons, including defective incipits and explicits.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="WadhMinasian_142-item1">
